inlineContent.text: with the property names to collect.
A JavaScript property name accumulator to accumulate the names of the object’s properties in.

code: void GetPropertyNames(JSContextRef ctx, JSObjectRef object, JSPropertyNameAccumulatorRef propertyNames);

inlineContent.text: callback only needs to provide the names of properties that the class vends through a custom
callback. The system adds other properties independently, including statically declared properties, properties that other classes vend, and properties that belong to the object’s prototype.
